snippet.title: Bowels of the Ocean - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Free Download: https://blakemckinnonproductions.itch.io/bowelsoftheocean

Bowels of the Ocean is a horror-themed underwater hunting sim made for the Haunted PS1 Summer Of Shivers. Descend into the depths of the ocean with your speargun to hunt fish and other aquatic life to feed an ancient, eldritch horror.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/blakemprods
